      "reason" : "BIGGEST_MUSIC_LISTENING_DAY",
      "title" : "The day you let Bollywood love songs set the sunrise and sunset",
      "description" : "From first light, you looped “Tum Se Hi” and “Mast Magan” in a gentle spiral, letting Pritam, A.R. Rahman, and Arijit Singh soundtrack the day. By evening, Ed Sheeran’s “Perfect” and “Mera Pehla Pehla Pyaar” wove through the familiar. 185 minutes, 38 tracks, 35 artists—your biggest music day, anchored by your annual favourites.",
