      "reason" : "MOST_NOSTALGIC_DAY",
      "title" : "The day you rewound to 2000s Bollywood before breakfast",
      "description" : "Overnight, you drifted through “Aaj Ki Raat” and “Dil Haara,” then let Pritam and Sonu Nigam guide a sunrise parade of 2000s filmi hits. Every track—“Mann Ki Lagan,” “Kasam Ki Kasam,” “Tu Aashiqui Hai”—felt like a familiar script. 95 minutes, 18 tracks, 29 artists—your most nostalgic day, pure throwback.",
